high_descs: Turn right and move forward, then turn right and go to the fridge, then turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the dishwasher.
Pick up the egg from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Clean the egg in the sink.
Turn around and go to the stove, then look up the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the egg inside, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in the microwave.
